INotifyComposablePartCatalogChanged Interface

Definition

Provides notifications when a ComposablePartCatalog changes.

In this Article

public interface INotifyComposablePartCatalogChanged

Events

Changed

Occurs when a ComposablePartCatalog has changed.

public event EventHandler<System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ComposablePartCatalogChangeEventArgs> Changed;

Changing

public event EventHandler<System.ComponentModel.Composition.Hosting.ComposablePartCatalogChangeEventArgs> Changing;
